      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさんが、スポーツカーのCMに出演が決まった）\n（それは、とてもめでたい話……だったんだが）",
      "startTime": 5.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 9.4
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 9.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……参ったわね。寝ても疲れが取れないどころか\nますます体が重くなってくる感じだわ",
      "startTime": 16.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "CM撮影まで、もうそんなに時間がないのに\nゆっくり休んでいられる余裕なんて…………っ！？",
      "startTime": 24,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 27.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんですか\n失礼しました、少しぼうっとしていて",
      "startTime": 31.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 35.1999984741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あの……mihoさん、大丈夫ですか……？\n何か顔色が悪いように見えますけど……けほっ",
      "startTime": 38.3666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "妙に肩が重いような、変な感覚があるだけです\nストレッチで解消するでしょうから、お気遣いなく",
      "startTime": 47.7333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 51.3333318074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ貴方こそ、咳をしてるじゃないですか\n忙しくても、体調管理はマネージャーの基本ですよ",
      "startTime": 55.9710652865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……この間から少し風邪気味で\nCM撮影までにはなんとかしておきます",
      "startTime": 63.1333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 66.3333318074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（……昨日、芽衣が「mihoちゃんに悪いのが）\n（憑いてる」って、怖いこと言ってたんだよな）",
      "startTime": 69.4666651408,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1133.333333400003,
          "startTime": 67.4666651408
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（肩が重いって……もしかして……）\n（いやでも、mihoさんに限ってそんなことないか）",
      "startTime": 76.8333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.0666651408
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.0666651408
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.2715856235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ。今日も打ち合わせが長引いてしまった……この道\n墓地のそばだから、夜遅くに通りたくないんだよなぁ",
      "startTime": 87.7666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばこの間千紗が怖い話をしてたな。真夜中に\n赤い車で墓地の周りを爆走する幽霊がいる……とか",
      "startTime": 97.7999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、まさかな……そもそも、幽霊が車なんて\n乗れるはずないし……けほっ…………あれ？",
      "startTime": 106.8666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 110.3666651408
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.4333257038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、赤い車が爆走してる！？　噂は本当だったのか！？\nしかもこっちに来た……！　うわ、轢かれる……！",
      "startTime": 116.8666651408,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4800.006103600012,
          "startTime": 116.2333318074
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8426.666704799998,
          "startTime": 119.8599924086
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.3999923705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "……え、{user}さん？\nこんな時間までお仕事ですか？　お疲れ様です",
      "startTime": 123.6333318074,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 193.3333714000014,
          "startTime": 120.5933257419
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.5666590372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "み、mihoさん……！？　びっくりした……\nなんで深夜に赤い車で徘徊してるんですか！",
      "startTime": 131.8666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "真っ青な顔で地面にへたり込んで一体どうしたんですか\nまるで人を幽霊みたいな目で見ないで下さい",
      "startTime": 139.5666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 142.7999923705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ、例のスポーツカーのCM撮影があるので\nここで運転の練習をしてただけですよ",
      "startTime": 147.5333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど……それにしても\nまさかmihoさんが幽霊騒動の犯人だったなんて……",
      "startTime": 154.2666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 158.0333257038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "幽霊騒動？　ああ、だからこの辺りは人気が\nないんですね。おかげで助かってます",
      "startTime": 163.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 166.9333257038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "運転の練習って、mihoさん免許は持ってるんじゃ？\nそれにこの間の口ぶりだとそんな必要なさそうですけど",
      "startTime": 172.3999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 176.8666590372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "……昔、葉ちゃんと旅行に行った後は\nあまり……いえ、ほとんど運転していないんです",
      "startTime": 180.2333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それは、ペーパードライバーと言うのでは……？\n無理して運転しなくてもいいって言ったじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 191.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 194.9999954223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "運転だけ出来ない、なんて情けないこと\nクライアントに言える訳がないでしょう",
      "startTime": 197.6666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 200.1333287556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "ともかくそういう訳で、レンタカーを借りて\nここ数日、この辺りをぐるぐる何周も走ってたんです",
      "startTime": 203.4097254203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、先日、警官に呼び止められまして\n事情を説明したら、なんだか同情されましたけど……",
      "startTime": 212.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 215.4999954223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど……それにしても\n墓地の近くなんて、怖くはなかったんですか？",
      "startTime": 219.1000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 222.566662089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
